{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"32c4ae26a6","title":"魏太星的右派言论","origin":"《右派言论集》（河南医学院马列主义教研室编印，1958年4月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"adcbb11937","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"32c4ae26a6"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"00d8e3d85b","name":"河南医学院"},{"id":"24c1fba5f8","name":"魏太星"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f10ff96937","type":"title","text":"魏太星的右派言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32c4ae26a6"},{"id":"b6d4ac6039","type":"authors","text":"河南医学院魏太星","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32c4ae26a6"},{"id":"6d72fafd52","type":"subtitle","text":"[魏太星：河南医学院内科基础教研组讲师、民盟盟员]","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32c4ae26a6"},{"id":"cc679a788b","type":"paragraph","text":"咱们医学院要弄好，非把卢长山撤职不可。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32c4ae26a6"},{"id":"ab57aed8e6","type":"paragraph","text":"他们(指党)是捧人捧到云彩眼里，踩人踩到脚底下。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32c4ae26a6"},{"id":"1364804c5b","type":"paragraph","text":"党员都是平时向党汇报的人，不敢得罪他们，得罪他们不利。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32c4ae26a6"},{"id":"d5b65653c4","type":"paragraph","text":"现在的社会是六亲不认，儿子不认父亲，妻子不认丈夫，家族不团结，社会不团结。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32c4ae26a6"},{"id":"b2d5b89190","type":"paragraph","text":"三反时没有报复不可能。当时我是工会主席，带头贴大字报，后来斗了我，这不是报复？","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32c4ae26a6"},{"id":"e2d27090e4","type":"paragraph","text":"党的整风运动是开门整风还是关门整风？还是半开半关？那小舅子才知道。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32c4ae26a6"},{"id":"c5b40f1647","type":"paragraph","text":"马列主义不一定作指导思想，马克思列宁都不是中国人。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32c4ae26a6"},{"id":"d60dc2501d","type":"paragraph","text":"“实践论”要是你写的，那就不会这么讨论。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32c4ae26a6"},{"id":"718532d983","type":"paragraph","text":"咱们医学院的干部太驯服了，若是别的地方早就干起来了。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32c4ae26a6"},{"id":"9a8292507a","type":"paragraph","text":"来一个老爷带一个太太，我认为都可以走，医学院留一个赵文定就行了，咱们学校有太太阶级，光拿钱不干活，不适合这里工作，叫她们(指女党员)回农村去。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32c4ae26a6"},{"id":"58c6ef73ed","type":"paragraph","text":"人事制度也要改，干部科只知掌握生死簿。咱学校会计科有一批黑名单，光拿钱不干活，都是太太阶级。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32c4ae26a6"},{"id":"1dbfb9e1a0","type":"paragraph","text":"党员为啥不鸣呢？他们不敢说话。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32c4ae26a6"},{"id":"853cbc5173","type":"paragraph","text":"啥“工人说话了”，还不是那几个人！","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32c4ae26a6"}],"page":{"id":"10e529baf9","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32c4ae26a6","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}